       t_set (next_frontier frontier vis) =
         (\<Union> {Pair_Graph.neighbourhood (Graph.digraph_abs G) u | u . u \<in> t_set frontier}) - t_set vis" and
   finite_neighb:
     "finite (Pair_Graph.neighbourhood (Graph.digraph_abs G) u)"
